<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>大三下 on Z2X BLOG</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/tags/%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%8B/</link><description>Recent content in 大三下 on Z2X BLOG</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.147.6</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.z2x-blog.top/tags/%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%8B/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>第十二章 图像模式分类</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/12%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%8C%E7%AB%A0-%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB/</link><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/12%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%8C%E7%AB%A0-%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB/</guid><description>图像模式分类是数字图像处理中的一个重要应用领域，涉及将图像中的对象或区域自动分配到预定义的类别中。</description></item><item><title>第十一章 表达和描述</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/11%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0-%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%92%8C%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0/</link><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/11%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0-%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%92%8C%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0/</guid><description>图像经过分割后，无论是关注其边界（外部轮廓）还是区域（内部属性），都需要用一种数学或特征形式将其“表达”和“描述”出来，以便后续的识别与理解。</description></item><item><title>第十章 图像分割</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/10%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E7%AB%A0-%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2/</link><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/10%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E7%AB%A0-%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2/</guid><description>图像分割是图像分析的第一步，其两大基石是图像像素的不连续性（边缘检测）和相似性（阈值和区域分割）。</description></item><item><title>计算机网络英文缩写速查表</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E7%BC%A9%E5%86%99%E9%80%9F%E6%9F%A5%E8%A1%A8/</link><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 09:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E7%BC%A9%E5%86%99%E9%80%9F%E6%9F%A5%E8%A1%A8/</guid><description>计算机网络课程笔记中出现的所有英文缩写及其全称、中文名称速查表，覆盖全部6章及CSMA/CA专题。</description></item><item><title>计算机网络简答题汇总</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AE%80%E7%AD%94%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AE%80%E7%AD%94%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>计算机网络简答题汇总</description></item><item><title>第六章 应用层</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD%E7%AB%A0-%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%B1%82/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 09:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD%E7%AB%A0-%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%B1%82/</guid><description>在计算机网络的五层协议体系结构中，&lt;strong>应用层&lt;/strong>位于最高层（第5层）。它的下层依次是运输层、网络层、数据链路层和物理层。</description></item><item><title>第八章 图像压缩</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/8%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AB%E7%AB%A0--%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%8E%8B%E7%BC%A9/</link><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 09:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/8%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AB%E7%AB%A0--%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%8E%8B%E7%BC%A9/</guid><description>数字图像基础</description></item><item><title>第五章 图像恢复与重建</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/5%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E7%AB%A0-%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D%E4%B8%8E%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA/</link><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/5%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E7%AB%A0-%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D%E4%B8%8E%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA/</guid><description>图像退化模型、噪声模型、空间域复原、频率域复原、退化函数估计、逆滤波、维纳滤波、约束最小二乘滤波、投影重建</description></item><item><title>第五章 运输层</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E7%AB%A0-%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E5%B1%82/</link><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E7%AB%A0-%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E5%B1%82/</guid><description>运输层向应用层提供进程之间的逻辑通信，屏蔽网络核心细节。</description></item><item><title>第三章 空间域图像增强</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/3%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%A0-%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%9F%9F%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA/</link><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/3%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%A0-%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%9F%9F%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA/</guid><description>图像增强的目标是处理图像，使它比处理前的图像更加适合于应用。</description></item><item><title>第四章 图像变换及频率域图像增强</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/4%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E7%AB%A0-%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%8F%98%E6%8D%A2%E5%8F%8A%E9%A2%91%E7%8E%87%E5%9F%9F%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA/</link><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/4%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E7%AB%A0-%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%8F%98%E6%8D%A2%E5%8F%8A%E9%A2%91%E7%8E%87%E5%9F%9F%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA/</guid><description>图像空间→变换域空间→图像空间</description></item><item><title>实验四 图像的频域滤波与傅里叶变换</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E5%9B%9B/</link><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E5%9B%9B/</guid><description>实验四</description></item><item><title>第四章 网络层</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E7%AB%A0-%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%B1%82/</link><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E7%AB%A0-%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%B1%82/</guid><description>第四章 网络层</description></item><item><title>实验三</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E4%B8%89/</link><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E4%B8%89/</guid><description>实验三</description></item><item><title>第二章 数字图像基础</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/2%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E7%AB%A0-%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</link><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 09:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/2%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E7%AB%A0-%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</guid><description>数字图像基础</description></item><item><title>第一章 概论</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/1%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0-%E6%A6%82%E8%AE%BA/</link><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/1%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0-%E6%A6%82%E8%AE%BA/</guid><description>从获取图像开始，历经增强、恢复、压缩、分割直到最终的目标识别分类，并掌握空间域和变换域两大基本方法框架。</description></item><item><title>第三章 数据链路层</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%A0-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E9%93%BE%E8%B7%AF%E5%B1%82/</link><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 09:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%A0-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E9%93%BE%E8%B7%AF%E5%B1%82/</guid><description>数据链路层在计算机网络体系结构中起着承上启下的关键作用。</description></item><item><title>第二章 物理层</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E7%AB%A0-%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E5%B1%82/</link><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E7%AB%A0-%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E5%B1%82/</guid><description>在计算机网络体系结构中，物理层处于最底层（OSI模型的第1层，TCP/IP模型的网络接口层底部）。</description></item><item><title>实验二</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E4%BA%8C/</link><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E4%BA%8C/</guid><description>灰度变换增强图像与图像的直方图统计</description></item><item><title>实验一 视觉感知现象验证与分析</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E4%B8%80/</link><pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E4%B8%80/</guid><description>视觉感知现象验证与分析</description></item><item><title>第一章 概述</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0-%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0/</link><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0-%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0/</guid><description>本章从宏观上带我们鸟瞰了计算机网络的全貌。</description></item></channel></rss>